ottom:1px solid black;'>" + data.location + "</td><td style='font-weight:bold;'>Inspection Date/Time:</td><td colspan='3' style='border-bottom:1px solid black;'>" + dateStr + "</td></tr></table></div><table class='checklist-table' cellspacing='0'><tr class='checklist-header'><td style='border:1px solid black; width:5%; text-align:center; padding:5px;'>S/N</td><td style='border:1px solid black; width:75%; text-align:left; padding:5px;'>ITEM</td><td style='border:1px solid black; width:20%; padding:5px;'>COMMENT</td></tr>" + itemsHtml + "</table><div style='margin-top:10px; font-size:11px;'><div style='margin-bottom:10px;'><b>Remarks: </b> <span style='border-bottom:1px dotted black; padding-right:100%;'>" + (data.remarks || "") + "</span></div><table style='width:100%; margin-top:20px; border:none;'><tr><td style='width:10%; font-weight:bold;'>Inspector:</td><td style='width:40%; border-bottom:1px dotted black;'>" + data.inspectedBy + "</td><td style='width:50%;'></td></tr><tr><td style='font-weight:bold;'>Inspector Sig:</td><td style='border-bottom:1px dotted black; height:30px; vertical-align:bottom;'>" + (data.signatures.inspector ? "<img src='" + data.signatures.inspector + "' style='height:25px;' />" : "") + "</td><td></td></tr><tr><td colspan='3' style='height:10px;'></td></tr><tr><td style='font-weight:bold;'>Driver:</td><td style='border-bottom:1px dotted black;'>" + data.driverName + "</td><td></td></tr><tr><td style='font-weight:bold;'>Driver Sig:</td><td style='border-bottom:1px dotted black; height:30px; vertical-align:bottom;'>" + (data.signatures.driver ? "<img src='" + data.signatures.driver + "' style='height:25px;' />" : "") + "</td><td></td></tr></table></div>" + (data.photos && (data.photos.damage || data.photos.front) ? "<div style='page-break-before:always; margin-top:20px;'><h3>Pictures:</h3><table style='width:100%; margin-top:10px;'><tr><td><b>Front:</b><div style='border:1px solid black; height:150px; text-align:center; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;'>" + (data.photos.front ? "<img src='" + data.photos.front + "' style='max-height:140px; max-width:100%;' />" : "N/A") + "</div></td><td><b>Left:</b><div style='border:1px solid black; height:150px; text-align:center; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;'>" + (data.photos.ls ? "<img src='" + data.photos.ls + "' style='max-height:140px; max-width:100%;' />" : "N/A") + "</div></td></tr><tr><td><b>Back:</b><div style='border:1px solid black; height:150px; text-align:center; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;'>" + (data.photos.back ? "<img src='" + data.photos.back + "' style='max-height:140px; max-width:100%;' />" : "N/A") + "</div></td><td><b>Damage:</b><div style='border:1px solid black; height:150px; text-align:center; display:flex; align-items:center; justify-content:center;'>" + (data.photos.damage ? "<img src='" + data.photos.damage + "' style='max-height:140px; max-width:100%;' />" : "N/A") + "</div></td></tr></table></div>" : "") + "</body></html>";
  },

  createPetroleumV2Report: function(data) {
      var dateStr = new Date(data.timestamp).toLocaleString('en-GB');
      var itemsHtml = "";
      var currentCategory = "";
      (data.items || []).forEach(function(item) {
          var parts = item.label.split('. ');
